    nodePosition:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 153
      y: 135
      width: 499
      height: 371
    soundEffect: {fileID: 0}
    backgroundMusic: {fileID: 0}
    likeGain: 0
    showLikeBar: 0
  - guid: fce215a7-155b-4712-9194-ea9cef39b9d9
    characterSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c983164e6fa82948968e14cd1200977, type: 3}
    characterName: "Voc\xEA"
    dialogueText: "Sim chefe, j\xE1 est\xE1 com ele. E eu tenho uma coisa pra fala-"
    backgroundSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ca3deff72af3854d882fcf4f1c66d37, type: 3}
    startNode: 0
    endNode: 0
    choices: 1
    choiceOptions:
    - 
    nodePosition:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 778
      y: 131
      width: 499
      height: 371
    soundEffect: {fileID: 0}
    backgroundMusic: {fileID: 0}
    likeGain: 0
    showLikeBar: 0
  - guid: deb98f72-55f2-4c8d-a6e6-856aeade9b7b
    characterSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c983164e6fa82948968e14cd1200977, type: 3}
    characterName: Chester
    dialogueText: "\xD3timo, espero que aquele pentelho n\xE3o demore. Estamos com
      muitas demandas desde que tudo foi conectado com os sat\xE9lites e os superiores
      tem nos enchido o saco com presta\xE7\xE3o de contas."
    backgroundSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ca3deff72af3854d882fcf4f1c66d37, type: 3}
    startNode: 0
    endNode: 0
    choices: 1
    choiceOptions:
    - 
    nodePosition:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 1363
      y: 125
      width: 499
      height: 371
    soundEffect: {fileID: 0}
    backgroundMusic: {fileID: 0}
    likeGain: 0
    showLikeBar: 0
  - guid: 6a70dc28-1b2b-4147-9ed4-a2935538126b
    characterSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c983164e6fa82948968e14cd1200977, type: 3}
    characterName: Chester
    dialogueText: "Pelo que sei, as coisas t\xEAm ficado um caos l\xE1 fora, tudo
      depois disso\u2026 bem, o importante \xE9 que o dinheiro est\xE1 entrando.
      O que voc\xEA tinha a dizer mesmo?"
    backgroundSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ca3deff72af3854d882fcf4f1c66d37, type: 3}
    startNode: 0
    endNode: 0
    choices: 1
    choiceOptions:
    - 
    nodePosition:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 1939
      y: 114
      width: 499
      height: 371
    soundEffect: {fileID: 0}
    backgroundMusic: {fileID: 0}
    likeGain: 0
    showLikeBar: 0
  - guid: 9a38cd4d-9e34-4682-9474-38653a47d88d
    characterSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c983164e6fa82948968e14cd1200977, type: 3}
    characterName: Chester
    dialogueText: "Pelo que sei, as coisas t\xEAm ficado um caos l\xE1 fora, tudo
      depois disso\u2026 bem, o importante \xE9 que o dinheiro est\xE1 entrando.
      O que voc\xEA tinha a dizer mesmo?"
    backgroundSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ca3deff72af3854d882fcf4f1c66d37, type: 3}
    startNode: 0
    endNode: 0
    choices: 2
    choiceOptions:
    - "Eu encontrei uma rob\xF4 na sala dos servidores. Ao menos \xE9 isso que ela
      diz ser."
    - "O senhor por acaso est\xE1 pensando em se aposentar?"
    nodePosition:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 2488
      y: 74
      width: 499
      height: 433
    soundEffect: {fileID: 0}
    backgroundMusic: {fileID: 0}
    likeGain: 0
    showLikeBar: 0
  - guid: 4b7bf64c-b9c4-4816-ae65-3b9a5b5973c8
    characterSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c983164e6fa82948968e14cd1200977, type: 3}
    characterName: Chester
    dialogueText: "\xC9 o que?? Andou bebendo? Como assim um rob\xF4, rapaz?"
    backgroundSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ca3deff72af3854d882fcf4f1c66d37, type: 3}
    startNode: 0
    endNode: 0
    choices: 1
    choiceOptions:
    - 
    nodePosition:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 3131
      y: -147
      width: 499
      height: 371
    soundEffect: {fileID: 0}
    backgroundMusic: {fileID: 0}
    likeGain: 0
    showLikeBar: 0
  - guid: 03ddb597-3078-4dfe-b9e1-5f1b23332a6e
    characterSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c983164e6fa82948968e14cd1200977, type: 3}
    characterName: "Voc\xEA"
    dialogueText: "Ah, \xE9 que um brotinho rob\xF4 falou que era minha nova chefe,
      ent\xE3o achei que o senhor j\xE1 estava pra se aposentar."
    backgroundSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ca3deff72af3854d882fcf4f1c66d37, type: 3}
    startNode: 0
    endNode: 0
    choices: 1
    choiceOptions:
    - 
    nodePosition:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 3708
      y: 285
      width: 499
      height: 371
    soundEffect: {fileID: 0}
    backgroundMusic: {fileID: 0}
    likeGain: 0
    showLikeBar: 0
  - guid: 4f126e26-169b-4b01-80c3-1db10864db9c
    characterSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c983164e6fa82948968e14cd1200977, type: 3}
    characterName: Chester
    dialogueText: "Que pergunta \xE9 essa do nada? Eu ainda n\xE3o irei me aposentar,
      apesar de velho."
    backgroundSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ca3deff72af3854d882fcf4f1c66d37, type: 3}
    startNode: 0
    endNode: 0
    choices: 1
    choiceOptions:
    - 
    nodePosition:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 3090
      y: 290
      width: 499
      height: 371
    soundEffect: {fileID: 0}
    backgroundMusic: {fileID: 0}
    likeGain: 0
    showLikeBar: 0
  - guid: 9bebac16-e928-4d9b-8317-db52cb8282fb
    characterSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c983164e6fa82948968e14cd1200977, type: 3}
    characterName: "Voc\xEA"
    dialogueText: "Estou dizendo a verdade, senhor! \xC9 um rob\xF4 aparentemente
      muito inteligente, capaz de conversar como um humano."
    backgroundSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ca3deff72af3854d882fcf4f1c66d37, type: 3}
    startNode: 0
    endNode: 0
    choices: 1
    choiceOptions:
    - 
    nodePosition:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 3730
      y: -157
      width: 499
      height: 371
    soundEffect: {fileID: 0}
    backgroundMusic: {fileID: 0}
    likeGain: 0
    showLikeBar: 0
  - guid: c2af2baa-9469-4868-b88c-4d06e2e031db
    characterSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c983164e6fa82948968e14cd1200977, type: 3}
    characterName: Chester
    dialogueText: "Vou verificar nas c\xE2meras de seguran\xE7a\u2026 MACACOS ME
      MORDAM O QUE \xC9 ISSO?? Realmente tem um rob\xF4 ali!"
    backgroundSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ca3deff72af3854d882fcf4f1c66d37, type: 3}
    startNode: 0
    endNode: 0
    choices: 1
    choiceOptions:
    - 
    nodePosition:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 4364
      y: -155
      width: 499
      height: 371
    soundEffect: {fileID: 0}
    backgroundMusic: {fileID: 0}
    likeGain: 0
    showLikeBar: 0
  - guid: 0eec18f5-c8b3-4625-a017-102ed8a92b74
    characterSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c983164e6fa82948968e14cd1200977, type: 3}
    characterName: Chester
    dialogueText: "Voc\xEAs ainda n\xE3o tem supervisor novo\u2026 mas espera, brotinho?
      Onde? Calma, um ROB\xD4????"
    backgroundSpr: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ca3deff72af3854d882fcf4f1c66d37, type: 3}
    startNode: 0
    endNode: 0
    choices: 1
    choiceOptions:
    - 
